    <!-- Instruction Dialog -->
    <string name="instructions_title">Instructions: %1$s</string>
    <string name="instructions_productive_morning">
1. Think about your main goal for today.
2. Set three priorities that matter most.
3. Note potential distractions and how to minimize them.

Tip: Try to describe each priority in one sentence.
    </string>
    <string name="instructions_goals">
1. Define your long-term goal (e.g., over the next 6 months).
2. Write down what you did today toward it.
3. Consider what steps you can take tomorrow.

Tip: Keep your thoughts in short bullet points.
    </string>
    <string name="instructions_evening_reflection">
1. Describe in a few sentences what stood out today.
2. How are you feeling now? Note your current impressions.
3. What did you learn from today’s experiences?

Tip: Try to write honestly and without judgment.
    </string>
    <string name="instructions_gratitude">
1. Think of three things you’re grateful for today.
2. Write each point out in one or two sentences.
3. Reflect on why those things matter to you.

Tip: Gratitude can be found in small everyday moments.
    </string>
    <string name="instructions_none">
